title: 3512 Savana Lane - 3 bedroom / 2.5 bathroom
posting_body: ['3512 Savana Lane is a two-level townhome located in the highly coveted Garden Isle Community of Alameda.', 'The 3-bedroom 2.5 bathroom offers a fantastic light-filled living-dining room combo, decorative fireplace, and large bedrooms including an exceptionally spacious suite with a large walk-in closet.', 'Kitchen features a stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, and disposal.', 'laundry room with washer/dryer in unit, private patio, and a large two-car garage.', 'HomeOwner Association amenities include a community center available for private parties and a large swimming pool.', '3512', 'Savana Lane is\xa0 centrally located with an easy stroll to the SF Bay Trail, with breathtaking views of the city, serene walks, or bike rides along the bay.', 'Top-performing public schools, a world-class golf course, local eats, shopping, bus lines & San Francisco trans bay ferry are all conveniently located nearby.', 'Property is professionally managed by Owner', 'Lease terms: 1 year lease', 'Rent: $3900', 'Security Deposit: $4600', 'Rental fee: One time 30% rental fee paid by tenant', 'No Pets', 'Tenants pays gas, electric, and garbage/recycle', '2 car garage', 'Washer/Dryer', 'Contact the CZRE leasing team to schedule a viewing.', 'show contact info', 'Due to the current COVID-19 restrictions and high volume of inquiries, please be patient with us.', 'Please note that our showing schedule is typically Monday-Friday 9am-4pm and weekends by appointment only.', 'To expedite your request, include property address in the subject line with a few dates and times that you are available to preview.', 'We look forward to getting you into this great community.', 'Do not disturb residents.', 'Cerda-Zein Real Estate, Inc is an equal housing opportunity company.', 'Listed by Cerda-Zein Real Estate, Lic #01878914', 'See more rentals at <URL>', 'All information deemed reliable but has not been verified or guaranteed.']
